<button class="accordion">Why are law and ethics important in the healthcare field?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Healthcare law and ethics will help ensure that medical care professionals, workers and staff are held accountable to the public. Ethical standards in medical care also promote other important moral and social values such as social responsibility, human rights, compliance with the law and patient safety.</p>
